### 🌍 Variables globales
@host = http://<PUBLIC_IP>     # ⬅️ Reemplaza <PUBLIC_IP> por la IP pública de tu ECS Task (sin puerto, usa 80 por defecto)
@id = 123456-test              # variable temporal para test de PUT/DELETE

### 🚀 1. Create a new Bitcoin position
POST {{host}}/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTCUSDT",
  "quantity": 0.25,
  "type": "buy",
  "date": "2025-10-12"
}

### 📋 2. Get all positions
GET {{host}}/items

### 🔍 3. Get position by ID
# 🟡 Reemplaza {{id}} con un ID real obtenido del GET anterior
GET {{host}}/items/{{id}}

### ✏️ 4. Update position by ID
PUT {{host}}/items/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTCUSDT",
  "quantity": 0.5,
  "type": "sell",
  "date": "2025-10-13"
}

### ❌ 5. Delete position by ID
DELETE {{host}}/items/{{id}}

### 🧭 6. Swagger Documentation (UI)
GET {{host}}/docs

### 🏠 7. Frontend (HTML interface)
GET {{host}}/
